From hadley at rice.edu  Fri Nov 18 14:28:31 2011
From: hadley at rice.edu (Hadley Wickham)
Date: Fri, 18 Nov 2011 07:28:31 -0600
Subject: [R-sig-eco] Bootstrapping with pseudo-replicates
In-Reply-To: <20111117150236.269170@gmx.net>
